These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: techno, r&b
1. Music-Genre:techno is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | techno |

 #################################
 
